>The direct message of</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2152354572/image_2152354572.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743094-if-market-shut-down-for-10-years-id-be-happy-to-own-these-2-stocks", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:15:00"}, {"id": "4743284", "title": "Market Snakes Follow Ladders", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture><img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Hand-drawn game Snakes and Ladders. Close-up.\" data-id=\"1248963397\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"></picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-credits\">OlgaKhorkova</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Canada's Venture Composite Index (a basket of economically sensitive micro-cap companies, 44% weighted in materials, 30% information technology, 15.74% in energy, 3.5% health care, 2.48% financials, 1.85% industrials, .58% communication services, and .32% consumer discretionary) appears to concur with former BoC head Stephen Poloz's recessionary assessment.</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1248963397/image_1248963397.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743284-market-snakes-follow-ladders", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:10:00"}, {"id": "4742856", "title": "QQQI: Don't Sleep On This Income-Producing ETF On Track To Exceed A 13% Yield", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Money growth\" data-id=\"1445810162\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1055px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">PM Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>This may not be the most exciting time to discuss income, as the markets are making new all-time highs. The <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SP500\" target=\"_blank\">S&amp;P 500</a> is almost at 6,100 and is up over 27% in 2024, while the <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COMP:IND\" title=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/COMP:IND\" target=\"_blank\">Nasdaq</a> is approaching 20,000</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1445810162/image_1445810162.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4742856-qqqi-dont-sleep-on-this-income-producing-etf-on-track-to-exceed-a-13-percent-yield", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 17:00:00"}, {"id": "4743273", "title": "Nano-X Imaging: Expanded FDA Clearance Paves The Path For Deployment", "description": "<figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Normal pediatric chest x-ray\" data-id=\"869557690\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"855px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">radiologist/E+ via Getty Images</p></figcaption></figure><div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Nano-X Imaging (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/NNOX\" title=\"Nano-X Imaging Ltd.\">NNOX</a></span>) is quite a stock enigma. Every few quarters, the shares of NNOX race higher on some positive news, only to see most of the gains dissipate over the following months.</p> <p>For example, back in March, NNOX shares more than</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/869557690/image_869557690.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743273-nano-x-imaging-expanded-fda-clearance-paves-the-path-for-deployment", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:45:46"}, {"id": "4743268", "title": "Skye Bioscience: Nimacimab Targets Safer Weight Loss, Speculative Buy", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Unrecognizable Black Lady Showing Abdominal Muscles Wearing Oversized Jeans Indoor\" data-id=\"1467665258\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Prostock-Studio</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <p>Skye Bioscience, Inc. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NASDAQ:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SKYE\" title=\"Skye Bioscience, Inc.\">SKYE</a></span>) is a biopharmaceutical company that develops advanced therapies for obesity and metabolic conditions. The company\u2019s flagship candidate is Nimacimab, which is progressing in its CBeyond Phase 2 trials. This is a peripheral cannabinoid receptor type 1 [CB1] inhibitor</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1467665258/image_1467665258.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743268-skye-bioscience-nimacimab-targets-safer-weight-loss-speculative-buy", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:32:55"}, {"id": "4743037", "title": "ZIM Integrated: Beware Of The Dividend Trap", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Aerial view of containers and container ship in sea\" data-id=\"1008180456\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1151px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"> </p> <p class=\"item-credits\">Michael H</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Zim: Recent Outperformance Might Not Last</h2> <p>Investors in leading asset-light container shipping ZIM Integrated Shipping Services Ltd. (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSE:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/ZIM\" title=\"ZIM Integrated Shipping Services Ltd.\">ZIM</a></span>) have outperformed the S&amp;P 500 (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPX\" title=\"S&amp;P 500 Index\">SPX</a>) (<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SPY\" title=\"SPDR\u00ae S&amp;P 500 ETF Trust\">SPY</a>) significantly since my previous update. <a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/article/4703893-zim-integrated-dont-be-fooled-again-by-the-freight-rates-surge\">In</a></p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1008180456/image_1008180456.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743037-zim-integrated-beware-of-the-dividend-trap", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:30:00"}, {"id": "4743266", "title": "SCHD Vs. QDPL: Which ETF For Equity Dividends?", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"ETF Exchange-Traded Funds investment with investor building a portfolio of financial assets on market such as stock, bonds, commodities, currencies. Capital management and finance.\" data-id=\"1346228515\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"1024px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w320 320w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg?io=getty-c-w240 240w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 768px) calc(100vw - 36px), (max-width: 1024px) calc(100vw - 132px), (max-width: 1200px) calc(66.6vw - 72px), 600px\" fetchpriority=\"high\"> </picture><figcaption><p class=\"item-caption\"></p> <p class=\"item-credits\">NicoElNino</p></figcaption></figure></p> <div class=\"inline_ad_placeholder\"></div> <h2>Introduction</h2> <p>The Schwab US Dividend Equity ETF (<span class=\"ticker-hover-wrapper\">NYSEARCA:<a href=\"https://seekingalpha.com/symbol/SCHD\" title=\"Schwab U.S. Dividend Equity ETF\u2122\">SCHD</a></span>) is an incredibly popular ETF in the income investing niche, but deeper into that niche is the newer, up-and-coming Pacer Metaurus US Large Cap Div Multiplier 400 ETF (</p>", "image": "https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/1346228515/image_1346228515.jpg", "link": "https://seekingalpha.com/article/4743266-schd-vs-qdpl-which-etf-for-equity-dividends", "pub_date": "2024-12-10 16:25:18"}, {"id": "4743263", "title": "Monolithic Power Systems: Big Growth At A Reasonable Price", "description": "<p><figure class=\"getty-figure\" data-type=\"getty-image\"><picture> <img src=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w750\" alt=\"Business, Growth, Data, Manager, Improvement, Making Money, Growth, Opportunity, Strategy, Audit\" data-id=\"2054524126\" data-type=\"getty-image\" width=\"1536px\" height=\"864px\" srcset=\"https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1536 1536w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1280 1280w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w1080 1080w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w750 750w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w640 640w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w480 480w, https://static.seekingalpha.com/cdn/s3/uploads/getty_images/2054524126/image_2054524126.jpg?io=getty-c-w3